          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "An munsahir's skin radiates heat like a forge's fire. A creature that starts its turn in the area must succeed at a DC 19 Fortitude save or become fatigued while it remains in the area. Creatures immune to environmental heat effects or with any fire resistance are immune.",
